Government Owned

This software was developed by or for the U.S. Air Force and is government-owned,
non-proprietary software. It is released under the same terms as the Open Mission
Systems (OMS) and Universal Command and Control Interface (UCI) standards from
which it derives.

Governed by the Open Architecture Collaborative Working Group (OACWG).
Contact: aflcmc.ase.architectures@us.af.mil
